quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  69,9,"Then Pharaoh and whoever was <span class="h">before him{1}</span>and the Overturned Cities{2}came up with grave offenses",footnotes:1:[<span class="qiraat-footnote">Qira’at: Abu ‘Amr, Al-Kesa’i and Ya’qub read it as: “Then Pharaoh and whoever was on his side and the…”</span>],footnotes:2:[The Overturned Cities of the people of Lot.]
  69,10,"and disobeyed the messenger of their Lord, so He seized them with an overpowering grip."
